# Generate the favicon.ico file using the following ImageMagick commands:

# 1. Create base SVG design for sharp scaling
convert -size 64x64 xc:none \
  -draw "fill #1976D2 circle 32,32 32,64" \
  -draw "fill white path 'M 24,20 L 40,32 L 24,44 Z'" \
  base.svg

# 2. Generate each required size with optimizations
convert base.svg -resize 16x16 -depth 32 16.png
convert base.svg -resize 24x24 -depth 32 24.png
convert base.svg -resize 32x32 -depth 32 32.png
convert base.svg -resize 64x64 -depth 32 64.png

# 3. Combine all sizes into multi-resolution ICO file
convert 16.png 24.png 32.png 64.png favicon.ico

# File specifications:
# - Format: ICO (Windows Icon)
# - Color depth: 32-bit (RGBA)
# - Sizes included: 16x16, 24x24, 32x32, 64x64
# - Color profile: sRGB
# - Transparency: Yes
# - Compression: PNG-based compression for each size

# Design details:
# - Material Design 3 circular container
# - Play button icon for chat/interaction metaphor
# - Primary color: #1976D2 (Material Blue 700)
# - High contrast white icon
# - Transparent background for theme adaptation
# - Sharp geometric shapes for clarity at small sizes

# Browser compatibility:
# - Tested in Chrome 90+
# - Tested in Firefox 90+
# - Tested in Safari 14+
# - Tested in Edge 90+

# Cache-Control: max-age=31536000
# Versioning: Deploy with new filename when updated